{"title":"Hezir","link":"/en/wol/d/r1/lp-e/1200002013","html":"<span id=\"page1105\" class=\"pageNum\" data-no=\"1105\" data-before-text=\"1105\"></span><strong>HEZIR</strong>(He&#x2B9;zir) [Pig; Boar].<strong>1. </strong>The priest whose paternal house was chosen by lot for the 17th of the 24 priestly service divisions organized toward the end of David&#x2019;s reign.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200002013/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\">1Ch 24:1,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200002013/0/1\" data-bid=\"1-2\" class=\"b\"> 3,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200002013/0/2\" data-bid=\"1-3\" class=\"b\"> 5-7,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200002013/0/3\" data-bid=\"1-4\" class=\"b\">&#xA0;15</a>.<strong>2. </strong>One of &#x201C;the heads of the people&#x201D; whose descendant, if not he himself, in Nehemiah&#x2019;s time supported the resolution to be true to Jehovah.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200002013/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">Ne 9:38;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200002013/1/1\" data-bid=\"2-2\" class=\"b\"> 10:1,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200002013/1/2\" data-bid=\"2-3\" class=\"b\"> 14,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200002013/1/3\" data-bid=\"2-4\" class=\"b\">&#xA0;20</a>."}